Movie star, Funke Akindele has celebrated her husband, JJC Skillz’s birthday as he became a year older on Saturday. Akindele, the AMVCA award winner who emerged the Best Actress in a comedy (Movie/TV series) for her performance in “Mom’s at War” at the 7th edition of the glamorous award, took to her Instagram handle to pen down loving message to her husband. She wrote:” Happy birthday my darling husband. The Lord will grant you longer life and good health. Thank you for being a sweetheart! ”Our home will always be peaceful and the Lord will continue to bless us. Enjoy your day my king,” she wrote. (NAN)